data.description: *ASK AGENT ABOUT INCENTIVES ON THIS HOME!!  Charming 3-bedroom home exuding warmth and comfort. Boasting tile floors throughout, the property emanates a soothing palette that guarantees relaxation, especially in the great room. The kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with chocolate-stained cabinets, lustrous granite counters, modern stainless-steel appliances, ambient recessed lighting, and a chic subway tile backsplash. For added convenience, a pantry is provided alongside a central island that also serves as a breakfast bar. Retreat to the main bedroom to find your personal sanctuary; it offers a private bathroom with dual sinks and a walk-in closet. Serene backyard features a sheltered patio - the ideal nook for peaceful afternoons. Seize this exceptional home offering today!
